<h2>Password changed successfully</h2>

<p>Hello {{name}},</p>
<p>Your password has been successfully changed.</p>

<div class="warning-box">
  <p><strong>⚠️ If you didn't make this change,</strong> please contact support immediately.</p>
</div>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
  <a href="{{frontendUrl}}/forgot-password" class="button" style="display: inline-block; background: #09090b; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 9999px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.01em; margin: 8px 0;">
    Reset password
  </a>
</div>
